init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The "World's Best Dad" mug is now the "World's Worst Dad" mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I would like to see a list of the top 10 worst step dads.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I wonder if there is a list of the worst step moms.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I imagine there are plenty of them out there.
